data.title: Canford Chambers (Canford Hall), 22 St Peters Road, Bournemouth, Dorset
data.meta_description:
Canford Hall was once home to the Loyal Bourne Lodge of Oddfellows, No. 4437; shared with National Insurance Approved Society, No 123; S.T. Meggitt, electrical engineer; Canford Hall Typewriting Institute; Keays & Keays, accountants; R. Balmer, apartment agency; and the Academy of Elecution & Mime.
	To the left stood the Cairns Memorial Home, YMCA.
